    <title>#25: Feature Req: Merge Raids</title>
    <description>&lt;p&gt;
I think it might be useful to be able to merge evetns.  For instance....in a dungeon, there may be many boss encounters.  I know that in many cases its common practice to treat each encounter as a seperate raid.  Becasue people come and go through out the corse of a dungeon.  And you only want to give credit to those who are actualy there.
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
What I would sugest is a feature that allows you to either merge log files, or select several raids and merge them into a single event.
&lt;/p&gt;
